function CreditCard(probs){ const numberC= probs.number const lastFour=numberC.slice((numberC.length-4), numberC.length) const divStyle = { backgroundColor: `rgb(${probs.r}, ${probs.g}, ${probs.b})` }; return(
{probs.type}
{lastFour}
Expires {probs.expirationMonth}/{probs.expirationYear}
{probs.bank}
{probs.owner}
) } export default CreditCard
